{"tid":1750331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何柱國：「暴動」是由美國總統特朗普首先提出  我水平比林鄭高得多","createTime":"2019-11-24T10:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T16:41:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"af861a28a6884093fc07ba0ef455223e5e0e87ef","tid":1750331,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:50:24.000Z","msg":"美國國會通過《香港人權與民主法案》，全國政協常委、星島新聞集團主席何柱國認為，這會為中美關係帶來變數，現時爭議已經達至外交層面，超越了香港特別行政區的管轄權，要由中央處理。他又指，曾向政府提出修例時機不對，惟行政長官林鄭月娥當時未有理會他的警告。<br />\n<br />\n何柱國接受在無線電視節目《講清講楚》訪問時，質疑香港沒有自由的說法，「言論係唔係自由？叫你唔好戴口罩，你都會戴，有無自由？咁何來無自由？」他又稱，「暴動」是由美國總統特朗普首先提出，而美國商會亦不支持《香港人權與民主法案》。<br />\n<br />\n何柱國又說，在6、7月前，曾經警告林鄭月娥修例時機不對，當時中美正在商討經貿合約，「你講呢氣法例添忙添亂，係增加麻煩，但佢嗰時唔相信，因為她天真」。<br />\n<br />\n對於最近有傳他為下任政府組班，何柱國否認有關傳言，強調自己對做官沒有興趣，指「到政府做甚麼？為林鄭月娥工作？我水平比她高得多，我幫她做甚麼？」他又認為現時香港社會處於複雜狀況，需要有平衡思想、及世界觸覺的人，才可看清情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nhttp :// <a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1644796/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E4%BD%95%E6%9F%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95-%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E8%AE%8A%E6%95%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1644796%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%259F%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2595%25B8&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KGsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=66efb939\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1644796%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E4%25BD%2595%25E6%259F%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%2595%25B8&h=7302263c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1644796/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E4%BD%95%E6%9F%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%87%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E6%B3%95-%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E8%AE%8A%E6%95%B8</a>"},{"pid":"7b3a2426514782bb885ab713f20da881bffc1021","tid":1750331,"uid":161726,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:55:13.000Z","msg":"自由係相對唔係絕對<br />\n我地比同一水平既地區比係冇咁自由<br />\n億萬富豪都講埋d冇邏輯既野<br />\n我可以乜都講，但講完會比國泰篤灰<br />\n我可以戴口罩，但戴完會可能犯法<br />\n咁又自唔自由?邊個先進國家會咁?<br />\n紐倫港邊度冇得選地區首長?"},{"pid":"1a66082830dd1bc0c6c3aeb458d8b66f87e253a1","tid":1750331,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2e90477e017552497d5ccd05d665133a0fcfd3","tid":1750331,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一堆膠論"},{"pid":"2de40ea31d5662bcc82417c8dc5e89db4ca94cff","tid":1750331,"uid":260817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T10:56:58.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n<br />\n催淚彈污染地圖上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1750298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1750298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0bdd2ed46f9fbad3260118e0995ec57a35290065"